snippet.textDisplay:
A powerful addition to the lore, to be sure, but... despite his literal attempt in the beginning of the video, he just couldn't catch lightning in a bottle as he did with his debut track. Still, it is a haunting little ditty. Some people just want to watch the world burn. And some like to hum while they do it. Is this a clue to the origin of Yoda's species? Could it be that he is, in fact, a troll? A f&@%ing space troll waiting at the edge of the bridge of enlightenment to torment those searching for the answers to the universe, with his crooked little stick? Could it be that we are all better off not knowing what he really is?
Still... It's better than anything Kanye has done in the last ten years. Big-ups, Yoda, you magnificent little green bastard!
